Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:19.90,Song,,0,0,0,,If only there were no tests,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:23.63,Song,,0,0,0,,School would've been a fun place for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.63,0:00:29.97,Song,,0,0,0,,I never cared much for studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.08,0:00:38.49,Song,,0,0,0,,I just stared out the window all through class,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.49,0:00:44.53,Song,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Always dreaming away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:52.47,Song,,0,0,0,,But if I'd at least taken English seriously,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:59.81,Song,,0,0,0,,By now I'd be some cool international girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.78,0:01:07.35,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study a little than not at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.01,0:01:12.88,Song,,0,0,0,,There must be at least one thing you're good at.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.53,0:01:22.53,Song,,0,0,0,,Better to study while you still have the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.53,0:01:28.17,Song,,0,0,0,,Realizing too late won't help you then.
