Comment: 0,0:22:30.30,0:22:30.33,Song,,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.27,0:22:40.02,Song,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget, looking up at the sky from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:48.49,Song,,0,0,0,,The morning sun so beautiful, on spring days, just us two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.46,0:22:56.66,Song,,0,0,0,,All the hardships and the sorrows,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.11,0:22:54.78,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:01.05,Song,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:23:04.84,Song,,0,0,0,,Carry them away gently from this hilltop,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.51,0:23:11.75,Song,,0,0,0,,together with the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:22.19,Song,,0,0,0,,This vast, blue sky—may it never change,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.19,0:23:31.77,Song,,0,0,0,,And may my dearest friends stay just the way they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:33.77,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\q2\an9\fs20\bord0.3\blur1\fnA-OTF Shin Go Pro B\pos(431.23,256)\c&HFDFDFD&}Translation \NEditing \NQuality check
